hopobject.body: What's your number? cual es el costo de levitra en mexico A man with a long criminal record and no known occupation, Knapp outwitted authorities by moving often and quickly with a heavy backpack across a mountainous region stretching for 180 miles. He covered his tracks or changed stolen footwear to confuse searchers. His legend grew over the years, but authorities say ransacking cabins doesn't make him a folk hero.
